description:
The Good Morning Football Crew share what impressed them most about the Cowboys and Titans’ wins (00:30). The gang also discusses what they learned from week 10 (26:01). Lastly, Kay Adams, Nate Burleson, Peter Schrager, and Kyle Brandt give you their underappreciated storylines (35:47). Be sure to check in every Wednesday to the GMFB podcast! Like, share, subscribe! (49:43)
